cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY. 

The paper deals with a real-time algorithm for obstacle detection and tracking using Lidar and Radar sensors, which are commonly used in robotics and autonomous vehicles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as they are related to perception and decision-making in autonomous systems. The paper also involves data processing and filtering, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
